  m_Name: ScenarioDataSO
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: "A New Beginning\nCongratulations! You have graduated from Cybnus
    University with a degree in Computer Science. Like many new graduates, finding
    a job hasn't been easy. After weeks of searching, you finally receive an offer
    from Aterra Media & Data Control. \n\nBefore accepting, you do some research.
    Surprisingly, very little information about the company is available. It's a
    private organization, yet its name appears repeatedly in government technology
    projects. Despite its frequent involvement, there are almost no public details
    explaining what the company actually contributes. From what you can gather, Aterra
    specializes in network infrastructure and internet data management.\L\n\"Maybe
    they help keep the internet safe... and ethical.\"\L\nWith no better opportunities
    and eager to start your career, you accept the offer.\nToday is your first day."
  CompanyHeirarchySprites: []
